27:14.560 --> 27:17.677
What? This is new.

27:18.640 --> 27:20.278
What are--?

27:22.920 --> 27:24.592
Ah.

27:32.320 --> 27:34.470
What the--?

27:44.680 --> 27:46.318
RYAN:
You're awake.

27:46.720 --> 27:49.951
OLD ANGEL: It's beating.
-lt was your fourth heart attack.

27:50.160 --> 27:53.709
