Pretty Skanky Woman.

28:09.080 --> 28:10.672
Angel?

28:12.320 --> 28:13.878
Fred?

28:22.280 --> 28:25.113
[FRED SOBS]

28:35.920 --> 28:39.037
CORDELlA:
