-What the hell you think you're doing?
-He bit me!

31:09.160 --> 31:10.388
BOYFRlEND:
Freak!

31:11.400 --> 31:12.719
[SCREAMS]

31:13.880 --> 31:15.074
Nice!

31:27.480 --> 31:31.473
-Bring it on. That all you got?
-What are you on?

31:31.680 --> 31:36.390
