33:34.480 --> 33:37.517
Just don't turn me in.

33:37.720 --> 33:42.271
Not gonna have to.
Your kid's signing in at reception.

33:42.480 --> 33:44.072
OLD ANGEL: My kid?
-Uh-huh.

33:46.920 --> 33:52.233
