35:24.280 --> 35:27.511
He's the one that's
been casting that spell.

35:27.720 --> 35:31.110
You're Angel? With that cologne?
I don't think so.

35:31.320 --> 35:33.231
Don't stake him.

35:41.280 --> 35:43.430
God, I love technology.

35:43.640 --> 35:45.278
Are you all right?

35:45.480 --> 35:48.074
I gotta pee.

35:48.400 --> 35:52.837
